72
00:03:36,720 --> 00:03:37,400
No.

73
00:03:39,000 --> 00:03:40,040
It's, Miss Luo.

74
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:43,360
Get lost!

75
00:03:47,120 --> 00:03:48,320
Luo Qing,

76
00:03:48,760 --> 00:03:49,720
I warned you

77
00:03:49,720 --> 00:03:51,720
